  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201404/cc595594eeb4484c93a96778d76af123.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<strong>沪江名师Giulia：Around the World: a Day in the Arctic</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">时间：3月13日（星期四）16：00 - 17：00</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">主讲老师：Giulia（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/14058560/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击进入老师部落&gt;&gt;</a>）</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">公开课地点：英语大厅（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk&gt;&gt;</a>）</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>名师简介：<br />\n\t</strong></span></span></p>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>Giulia老师</strong>是美国意大利混血，母亲来自美国、父亲来自意大利。成长于欧洲和美国的她，已经在中国生活了近四年。她会说包括英语、意大利语、法语、西班牙语在内的多国语言，并正在努力学习中文。她很喜欢关于语言和文化的一切。</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #b22222;\"><strong>课堂内容提要：</strong></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><strong>一、Pronunciation Practice</strong></span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>CDs vs. cities</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span><strong>二、讨论：</strong></span></p>\n<div>\n\t<span>1.St.Patrick's Day = March 17th</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2.What do you know about the Arctic?&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>3.What words make you think of the cold?</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;refrigerator vs. freezer</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>usually the freezer is under the refrigerator.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>Ocean Canada&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>4.Cultures of the Arctic: the Inuit</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">三、介绍：</span></strong></span></p>\n<div>\n\t<span>&middot;Location</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>The Arctic consists of the Arctic Ocean, and parts of Canada, Russia, the US(Alaska), Denmark, Greenland,Norway, Sweden, Finland and Iceland.</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">四、Vocabulary 单词：</span></strong></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Adapt 适应</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Harsh 严酷、严厉、恶劣</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Indigenous : It happens naturally in a environment</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Indigenous people 土著人</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Coastal ： by the cost 沿海的</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Ancestors : something in the past from which something else has developed 祖先</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&middot;Hunt : to look for 猎、捕食、捕猎</span></span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Tundra 冻原、苔原</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Kayak&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>&middot;Marine ： relating to the sea&nbsp;</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/app/event\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>最新活动预约</strong></a></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; he